  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Minimum density (2 grains/sec) with 20ms Tukey window grains. At 12 simultaneous voices, approximately 24 grains arrive per second total — each audible as a brief discrete event separated by substantial silence. Tukey window preserves transient content at 50% flat-top. Very high reverb mix means each grain's tail overlaps with the silence before the next grain. The space between is the instrument.",
